## Changelog
### Features
* 500c677cc7b8132a54c7e48d816355487cf6cfbc feat: Add git-auto-commit and git-auto-push hooks
* fcf2ced17b410eece9bddb60974289cc44d36c28 feat: Add warnf template function
* 8540b4e8b0488c4f8743c01290c3c56e185d9bdf feat: Show original URL in HTTP progress bars
* 8b42ee8215927cb647db8baa963d6f6434886c4a feat: Support filenames containing # in ignore and remove files
### Fixes
* 5cbbd6e154fd2a03d71135f223465a1d045f73a6 fix: Fix persistent state mode for commands that execute templates
* 309d7fd719cf8d3be60fd0b2770929965165bf39 fix: Warn, don't error, when generating git commit messages for unknown states
### Documentation updates
* 0185fb8da635c9f991bf69531ed6b7c4687a895c docs: Add link to article
* 70546ad981e11369a824608f2c3ab8b0afa2a70a docs: Update pruneEmptyDicts example
* bd026f60bcc52ca3f9df0585df532f2b52761454 docs: Add link to article
* 8131e3f509b8091071922db0898f9e1c9c1d9ecf docs: Add link to article
